ent\">\n            <p>Yes, same premium formula with Jojoba, Sweet Almond, Avocado, Castor Oils, and Fragrance.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-header\">How do I recycle the Beard Oil Sample Kit packaging?<\/button>\n        <div class=\"accordion-content\">\n            <p>\n                • Magnetic box: Reuse or recycle.<br>\n                • Foam inserts: Repurpose if possible.<br>\n                • 10ml glass bottles: Recyclable, separate pipette components.\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-header\">What makes the Beard Oil Sample Kit special?<\/button>\n        <div class=\"accordion-content\">\n            <p>\n                • Variety of scents in one purchase.<br>\n                • Practical, luxurious option to upgrade grooming routine.<br>\n                • Ideal for gifting or discovering your favorite scent.\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <p style=\"margin-top:20px;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/beardandbones.co.uk\/pages\/faq-2\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#1E90FF;\">Learn more<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n<style>\n.sample-kit-faq-container {\n    background: #111;\n    color: #fff;\n    padding: 20px;\n    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    max-width: 600px;\n    margin: 20px auto;\n}\n.sample-kit-faq-container h2 {\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n    text-align: center;\n}\n.sample-kit-faq-container .accordion-item {\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n}\n.sample-kit-faq-container .accordion-header {\n    width: 100%;\n    background: #222;\n    color: #fff;\n    padding: 10px;\n    text-align: left;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    border: none;\n    border-radius: 5px;\n    font-size: 16px;\n}\n.sample-kit-faq-container .accordion-content {\n    display: none;\n    padding: 10px;\n    background: #333;\n    border-left: 3px solid #fff;\n    border-radius: 0 0 5px 